{"word":"καταμιαίνω","slug":"καταμιαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταμιαίνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ᾰνῶ</el>) </el><p/><i>to taint, defile</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to wear squalid garments</i> as a sign of grief, <i>wear mourning</i> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>sordidatus)</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}